[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 0,
        "end_time": 7000,
        "text": "Translator: Jennifer Cody\nReviewer: Jessica Ruby"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 6389,
        "end_time": 8055,
        "text": "When faced with a big challenge"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 8055,
        "end_time": 11336,
        "text": "where potential failure seems\nto lurk at every corner,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 11336,
        "end_time": 14228,
        "text": "maybe you&#39;ve heard this advice before:"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 14228,
        "end_time": 16419,
        "text": "&quot;Be more confident.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 16419,
        "end_time": 19530,
        "text": "And most likely, this is what you think\nwhen you hear it:"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 19530,
        "end_time": 22261,
        "text": "&quot;If only it were that simple.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 22261,
        "end_time": 24322,
        "text": "But what is confidence?"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 24322,
        "end_time": 28086,
        "text": "Take the belief that you are valuable,\nworthwhile, and capable,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 28086,
        "end_time": 30136,
        "text": "also known as self-esteem,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 30136,
        "end_time": 34769,
        "text": "add in the optimism that comes\nwhen you are certain of your abilities,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 34769,
        "end_time": 36820,
        "text": "and then empowered by these,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 36820,
        "end_time": 40869,
        "text": "act courageously \nto face a challenge head-on."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 40869,
        "end_time": 42857,
        "text": "This is confidence."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 42857,
        "end_time": 46684,
        "text": "It turns thoughts into action."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 46684,
        "end_time": 49480,
        "text": "So where does confidence even come from?"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 49480,
        "end_time": 52632,
        "text": "There are several factors \nthat impact confidence."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 52632,
        "end_time": 55492,
        "text": "One: what you&#39;re born with,\nsuch as your genes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 55492,
        "end_time": 60466,
        "text": "which will impact things like the balance\nof neurochemicals in your brain."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 60466,
        "end_time": 63037,
        "text": "Two: how you&#39;re treated."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 63037,
        "end_time": 66354,
        "text": "This includes the social pressures\nof your environment."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 66354,
        "end_time": 69563,
        "text": "And three: the part you have control over,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 69563,
        "end_time": 71038,
        "text": "the choices you make,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 71038,
        "end_time": 72516,
        "text": "the risks you take,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 72516,
        "end_time": 76653,
        "text": "and how you think about \nand respond to challenges and setbacks."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 76653,
        "end_time": 80385,
        "text": "It isn&#39;t possible to completely untangle\nthese three factors,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 80385,
        "end_time": 83955,
        "text": "but the personal choices we make\ncertainly play a major role"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 83955,
        "end_time": 86039,
        "text": "in confidence development."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 86039,
        "end_time": 89573,
        "text": "So, by keeping in mind \na few practical tips,"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 89573,
        "end_time": 95419,
        "text": "we do actually have the power to cultivate\nour own confidence."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 95419,
        "end_time": 98023,
        "text": "Tip 1: a quick fix."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 98023,
        "end_time": 101307,
        "text": "There are a few tricks that can give you\nan immediate confidence boost"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 101307,
        "end_time": 103008,
        "text": "in the short term."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 103008,
        "end_time": 106767,
        "text": "Picture your success \nwhen you&#39;re beginning a difficult task,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 106767,
        "end_time": 109723,
        "text": "something as simple as listening to music\nwith deep bass;"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 109723,
        "end_time": 113546,
        "text": "it can promote feelings of power."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 113546,
        "end_time": 118554,
        "text": "You can even strike a powerful pose\nor give yourself a pep talk."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 118554,
        "end_time": 123824,
        "text": "Tip two: \nbelieve in your ability to improve."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 123824,
        "end_time": 126013,
        "text": "If you&#39;re looking for a long-term change,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 126013,
        "end_time": 129895,
        "text": "consider the way you think \nabout your abilities and talents."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 129895,
        "end_time": 132243,
        "text": "Do you think they are fixed at birth,"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 132243,
        "end_time": 135100,
        "text": "or that they can be developed,\nlike a muscle?"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 135100,
        "end_time": 138193,
        "text": "These beliefs matter because\nthey can influence how you act"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 138193,
        "end_time": 140594,
        "text": "when you&#39;re faced with setbacks."
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 140594,
        "end_time": 142263,
        "text": "If you have a fixed mindset,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 142263,
        "end_time": 144881,
        "text": "meaning that you think your talents\nare locked in place,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 144881,
        "end_time": 146520,
        "text": "you might give up,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 146520,
        "end_time": 150216,
        "text": "assuming you&#39;ve discovered \nsomething you&#39;re not very good at."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 150216,
        "end_time": 154652,
        "text": "But if you have a growth mindset\nand think your abilities can improve,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 154652,
        "end_time": 158343,
        "text": "a challenge is an opportunity\nto learn and grow."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 158343,
        "end_time": 160821,
        "text": "Neuroscience supports the growth mindset."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 160821,
        "end_time": 166028,
        "text": "The connections in your brain do get\nstronger and grow with study and practice."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 166028,
        "end_time": 168209,
        "text": "It also turns out, on average,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 168209,
        "end_time": 171322,
        "text": "people who have a growth mindset\nare more successful,"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 171322,
        "end_time": 173054,
        "text": "getting better grades,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 173054,
        "end_time": 176529,
        "text": "and doing better \nin the face of challenges."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 176529,
        "end_time": 179751,
        "text": "Tip three: practice failure."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 179751,
        "end_time": 182406,
        "text": "Face it, you&#39;re going to fail sometimes."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 182406,
        "end_time": 184562,
        "text": "Everyone does."
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 184562,
        "end_time": 187421,
        "text": "J.K. Rowling was rejected by\ntwelve different publishers"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 187421,
        "end_time": 189798,
        "text": "before one picked up &quot;Harry Potter.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 189798,
        "end_time": 193236,
        "text": "The Wright Brothers built on history&#39;s\nfailed attempts at flight,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 193236,
        "end_time": 194903,
        "text": "including some of their own,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 194903,
        "end_time": 197635,
        "text": "before designing a successful airplane."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 197635,
        "end_time": 202303,
        "text": "Studies show that those who fail regularly\nand keep trying anyway"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 202303,
        "end_time": 205413,
        "text": "are better equipped to respond \nto challenges and setbacks"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 205413,
        "end_time": 208176,
        "text": "in a constructive way."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 208176,
        "end_time": 210515,
        "text": "They learn how to try \ndifferent strategies,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 210515,
        "end_time": 212226,
        "text": "ask others for advice,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 212226,
        "end_time": 214223,
        "text": "and perservere."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 214223,
        "end_time": 217017,
        "text": "So, think of a challenge \nyou want to take on,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 217017,
        "end_time": 219749,
        "text": "realize it&#39;s not going to be easy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 219749,
        "end_time": 221929,
        "text": "accept that you&#39;ll make mistakes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 221929,
        "end_time": 224341,
        "text": "and be kind to yourself when you do."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 224341,
        "end_time": 229511,
        "text": "Give yourself a pep talk, \nstand up, and go for it."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 229511,
        "end_time": 232887,
        "text": "The excitement you&#39;ll feel knowing that\nwhatever the result,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 232887,
        "end_time": 236223,
        "text": "you&#39;ll have gained greater knowledge\nand understanding."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 236223,
        "end_time": 238247,
        "text": "This is confidence."
    }
]